org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.game

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.svvrl.goal.core.AbstractEditable

    public class Game
extends Automaton
    A Game is a two-player game. The players are GamePlayer#P0 and GamePlayer#P1.
    Author:
    Ming-Hsien Tsai
